Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,82)}冈王花！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,74)}出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(628,64)}千波是个不挑食 是元气满满的孩子哦！
