Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(620,68)}是肉食淫花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,66)}啊 要被小冈吃掉了！
